text: Sekal Has to Die (; ) is a 1998 Czech World War II drama movie directed by Vladimír Michálek and starring Bogusław Linda, Olaf Lubaszenko, Agnieszka Sitek, Jiří Bartoška, Vlasta Chramostová, L'udovít Cittel. == Other websites == * Category:1998 drama movies Category:1990s war movies Category:Czech drama movies Category:World War II movies
title: Sekal Has to Die
